管安全。要全面分类整治，逐户逐栋排查，「一栋一策」整改。严厉打击危及建筑安全的违法行为，严格落实安全责任。健全长效机制，强化设计施工队伍、房屋鉴定机构和从业人员监管。会议强调，要抓紧推进全国安全生产大检查，主动排查和消除各类安全隐患，强化城市火灾防治等工作，坚决扭转事故多发局面。要坚持稳中求进、统筹全局，把各项工作做细做实。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-3398f9302bc0d38f8e924523c91744db_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "22 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/531779450"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I9YH2jsXa+ohYEAMaCDgwNDU1MjY3IMWx2ZMGMAE45gFALnIJNTMxNzc5NDUweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_1652051336.0343451", "card_id": "Q_521512691", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 55}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "法考考上 A 证的朋友们有什么建议啊？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "准备法考中，但是有点焦急了，很怕自己过不了，很怕没有达到自己的预期，很怕辜负父母的期望。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-c3d97b303b6788193ee0b62906c23c7b_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "21 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/521512691"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I9YH2jsXa+ohYEAMaCDc4MTczNDkwII+fsZEGMAE4rAFAL3IJNTIxNTEyNjkxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1652051336.034836", "card_id": "Q_531465323", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 39}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些小众不俗气文案适合母亲节?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picb.zhimg.com/50/v2-3d1608cc7a0ea99741a90d2d2d45347c_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "20 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/531465323"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I9YH2jsXa+ohYEAMaCDgwMzg1NTY5IKCUzpMGMAA4L0Awcgk1MzE0NjUzMjN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1652051336.035202", "card_id": "Q_531896625", "feed_specific": {"answer_co